Package com.gaminghub.app.presentation.model

Class CustomerModel

java.lang.Object
com.gaminghub.app.presentation.model.CustomerModel
public class CustomerModel extends Object
Represents a domain model for a customer in the system.

This model mirrors the `customers` table and includes key customer information such as name, email, and the account creation timestamp. It is primarily used in the presentation layer and can be converted to a CustomerEntity for persistence in the data layer.
